item.title: Hello!
item.description: So uh yeah, I have a blog now, I’m going to mostly use it for just rambling shit that might be useful to some people, and sometimes just to personally remember something i might find useful and would like to share. This isn’t really a conventional kind of blog, its more of a journal-ish thing, but yeah this should be fun :D
